text.data-name: Powerful facial recognition systems such as XiDs are much faster than other forms of ID.
Besides our core face recognition technology our FaaSTM can also help to seamlessly capture digital information from a vast portfolio of access control devices

FaaSTM provides the entry level capture of digital information for Cloud computing. Our network of standardized access control devices eliminate the need for costly and inefficient system integrators.

FaaSTM offers a wide range of services that range from Access Control, Time & Attendance, Claims, Bookings, Leave Management, Events Management as well as customized face recognition applications on the Cloud.
